d on public classes for private fields and setting them accessible, which is important.\n\n**Inspecting untracked files**\n\nI can't use tools to delete files, except maybe with bash commands. But wait, I don't think I need to remove the test file. There seems to be an untracked metadata directory, so I want to check that out since the status indicates it’s untracked. It could be from the prompt not being tracked, but the rule is not to modify anything. I should clarify in the final mention about the existing untracked files.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_074b68215ec426660169fee0eb434c81a3ac20fb161d6c44ab\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_uD8_kFZuOT3hsXFv3AWg93BgDRpqAOeuH3laEULxOqyGCdMdoxYNcCf5OQ3F2Q7qnbgZIIvCQP5A7XwcxynbhcvrcyUyxOgg7BQKzjEuJGHMe_c3ClI5XI2Lp8AK9CTAtESRVHUFX7Q2GJtERXPQnL56CvoCotvS-AOu3aifMRYQ0VNHlUVnnGEO5akhJg9rxQeV1NOCCzy_EsVVLhR1a6spVmmNPj0YgLfAp4h4o7EdC-iyH3IcJRPcx4dygA1Bxj8PKeSOajU7Wqo2jlftpd3X8jpal4h5SxgAu-YzdtLaRx5vJK4B6W-0UKJGC5NBvY8erorYft1UnYfcSciTDLIxSZVARrcpKvtiO_bNdTQy9D5C9UuLMLBr3C2yyWZV_FgxUku-OBnSIgbXDpH2FSs6DVbhuq1TQI3IKtH41m8HXB5WHUBgeldBRj9_va9-gU-WtTdokO33TFP7rWqHcr2vEdUTeruLpuUDkbGpdq7ePS1LmACSEPC378qnZGEhwx-Nh5OUTfIC_e_G-EAlZqfPFsW4h2TA5R-u2_9NwdTt-Gg2gSoKPQNGQzLcagVDLPTtEmFttSeVog5nSk_bjUKo2t2df56rCt49ywXVfNTYHRQpYUiYI4Ll_3RnYV97uiqYdaa2b60xxfS6_gVDQSvndQwvgsoJEw-NMNyVDSzfec_p0UY3M1qfLVtvyC--juSiNeutRrMXn0uBHKnc55hL-yhWFQ53ILwsLjLOe-tS7ZNR86HyE4simaKJUM9dQRwSMg8f4_fIVjD-6hX9hsspnxKQT4AoCB9r7GD4Ym5YhV6XYyRmChEVYiy0kALLFcS0AXmlnl3weecNOXdiBrh-guWi6sJC99OAnqNcfAZp4BW0-HO9QxuVUS6OhbxdcZTsWOWOK-Zxk7nKsSseK4rp8IDGob2CYTwRCYtXjV3hURqt-vlKObL_WheOlkLcfro6rN32j4AEqxTbf0uIELOJUWSyhMOSt7dXmy9V573UM0kPlW4K6bNEhZGXne2-SdNE-QJml5pTyC6XunBzYh76KuGjoHevjqUBjGSolOU2x7ZYDBBKiON18ofwKjzqx5_FJdY8dRHp8JQenSWupqruN-8hP5fld77uLG4dR0MpBkuUrJl3PpVdrG_qPMCp_WbTcG6-YRSl7V2HNmo3X7dSN7F4Lu4fpOV-WzdL-ghXKE5PiRyH-RR1xePKyk_63WBW8VEN2fmIekVOqTWWXytsrrAB9jgkvJSc3NoxvBokrsbKE2wAjlHKkohEK4pAGKQ6SmPkui8XowVi-1rDj6evW6GfRoRWRFccZxh05y